    "description": "《玛莎拉镇物语》是一款由Sugar Star★开发，BokiBoki Games发行的日式可爱风格全年龄向RPG游戏！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168490/extras/2dea769f720abe7a813170278f6c0cea.avif?t=1768962304\" width=600 height=432 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >故事</h2><br>这里是玛莎拉镇<br>是一个很少有游客来访的寂寥小镇。<br><br>小镇的出生率持续下降，年轻人也离开了小镇，前往都市。<br>长期支撑小镇的老人们都更老了，人口老化的越来越严重。<br>再这样下去小镇是不是会这样消失..<br><br>镇长决定，要为这个小镇注入新血。<br>为了挖掘这个小镇的所有魅力，研究地理并查找民间传说。<br>各种调查的结果，在这里有着有许多稀少又罕见的石头。<br>如果建造一间博物馆并展示这些稀有石头，人们肯定会聚集在这个小镇上！<br><br>因此我、达卡拉玛‧吉耶尔（茱兒）被派遣到这个小镇上，努力的挖掘稀有矿石！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168490/extras/0bbdd1e128f5443dce80bd55516dda92.avif?t=1768962304\" width=180 height=180 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168490/extras/790244a454218e89d17354a0da1e2ab6.avif?t=1768962304\" width=180 height=180 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168490/extras/c777969393d20f008c83978b3d0d7007.avif?t=1768962304\" width=180 height=180 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168490/extras/41027079853d9899098f4db22af44d36.avif?t=1768962304\" width=180 height=180 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168490/extras/01d03f592eb53bd1e336cdb478408a61.avif?t=1768962304\" width=180 height=180 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168490/extras/41cb1f9889d6534b6f99c7d26facfebc.avif?t=1768962304\" width=180 height=180 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168490/extras/87c956d0b43be67776f61c41c1a7dfc0.avif?t=1768962304\" width=600 height=340 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2168490/extras/d6edec43c61767fdf7249c4a27fffc02.avif?t=1768962304\" width=600 height=444 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>轻松小镇RPG游戏<br></li><li>探索地图<br></li><li>收集各种石头<br></li><li>提升城镇声望<br></li><li>提高居民的好感度<br></li><li>升级你的装备<br></li><li>与各种怪物战斗</li></ul>   ",
